<paragraph id="19C17C3AA5850621A86AF9B8A58A3837" pageNumber="33">
Geographic distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="9F8DB40D0389E9E5691E9DFFCB9DF462" LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:CF345025-EF7E-432B-B370-B010B63DB47E" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sebastidae" genus="Trachyscorpia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Trachyscorpia Mesoscorpia eschmeyeri Whitley 1970:245" order="Scorpaeniformes" pageNumber="33" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eschmeyeri" subGenus="Mesoscorpia">T. (M.) eschmeyeri</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
